title: SEMA.Battle.of.the.Builders.2014.HDTV.x264.mp4
description:
SEMA: Battle of the Builders




This one-of-a-kind build off -hosted by Overhaulin's AJ and SEMA President and CEO Chris Kersting, features the best builders from all over the world pitted against each other for the title of Top Builder.

More than 160 of the SEMA Show's top vehicles along with 125 individual vehicle builders and car customizers entered the first ever Battle of the Builders Competition in 2014. The TV show goes behind the scenes of what the expert judges had to say and how they narrowed it down to just 10 finalists. The finalists then selected from amongst themselves who would be named Top Builder at the inaugural SEMA Ignited event. The TV special also chronicles the builders' journey and showcases the trials and tribulations that the builders encountered along the way. Find out who has what it takes to be crowned the winner and join them on their journey through the competition.




Original Air Date: 08-Mar-2015
